{"tid":1309243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］小西灣需要人","createTime":"2019-07-12T06:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:33:08.000Z","uid":49462,"like":55,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b07f130ef8867e4ec694a6e18d474b302d0b2620","tid":1309243,"uid":49462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"大家好又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然大家都係度講緊唔好推咁多連儂牆既post<br />\n想將個焦點集中返係遊行同集會<br />\n先會引起更大既社會回響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我都同意既 所以首先幫大家宣傳下先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">13/7 光復上水！！<br />\n14/7 沙田大遊行！！</span></span><br />\n希望大家都可以積極參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n講返小西灣嘅問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有手足今日發現連儂牆就比人徹底破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家既天橋可能真係遍空白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/br9hufu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbr9hufu.png&h=27066c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先好抱歉 因為我地好難去派人手日日夜夜看守住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人破壞都只不係時間既問題<br />\n<br />\n但係我希望各位街坊唔好因爲咁就氣餒<br />\n亦唔好因爲冇人貼就唔寫唔貼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連儂牆係屬於大家<br />\n所以應該交返比大家守護</span><br />\n<br />\n我地雖然阻止唔到人地去撕<br />\n不過人地都阻止唔到我地貼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撕一 貼百</span><br />\n<br />\n希望各位企街坊能夠企出黎<br />\n再次重新築起屬於大家既連儂牆<br />\n改善屬於自己既社區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYjYdHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYjYdHB.png&h=41e88ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nthu4Pm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnthu4Pm.png&h=eca74264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a85a839e6b3c0277df9ffbb39542d82207061e0","tid":1309243,"uid":269065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"去緊喇 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70fdc0cd70eb15073ff8212115ba3f7a5bedb36","tid":1309243,"uid":232748,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3541d935fa547f5024517516b85a52a7a4a1c6","tid":1309243,"uid":232748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"f3ad3c3673b6363c54dd7da6fdd43d9ab157660d","tid":1309243,"uid":49462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7daf78bfe70f76678422d0686ec5a9c3426fc6","tid":1309243,"uid":49462,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b70fdc0cd70eb15073ff8212115ba3f7a5bedb36","tid":1309243,"uid":232748,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得唔好有衝突<br />\n安全至上"},{"pid":"805c2c672fd6bdfb816d54a591fa4f6e95e2833e","tid":1309243,"uid":49462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />